parameters: Do you want to teleport to the entrance?

Hermaphrodites are creatures equal to
gods. They possess both male and female
reproductive functions and are filled
with powerful magic.

Their immense magical power is highly
valued as offerings to the gods, and
those who possess both sexes are called
saints and have been offered as
sacrifices for generations.

In modern times, it is prohibited, but
even now in the church, those who
possess both sexes are chosen as holy
maidens.
Let's try looking for other books.
Effy: Hehehe... You finally came, huh.

Effy: I've been waiting for you,
Zerachiel.
Saint Effy: You are foolish, aren't you.

Saint Effy: I didn't think you would
invade again after experiencing such
humiliation.

Saint Effy: I really can't understand
you.

Zerachiel: The reason for your intrusion
again? It's obvious, isn't it.

Zerachiel: It's because I want revenge
on you!!
Zerachiel: I can't afford to lose.

Zerachiel: I have killed many lives for
that person.

Zerachiel: I've been prepared to receive
a lot of resentment a long time ago.
Zerachiel: And yet, you're giving up...?
Zerachiel: I apologize for taking lives.

Saint Effy: Are you, who has killed so
many lives, lecturing me?

Zerachiel: Ah, that's right. This is my
determination to fight, Effy.

Zerachiel: For the lives I have taken,
and for my own sake...
Effy: I don't think you can do it...
Effy: Let's make our partner happy.

Zerachiel: As an angel, I declare to
you.

Zerachiel: Saint Effy, I shall bestow
divine punishment upon you!!

Zerachiel: It's time to settle this,
Effy!!

Zerachiel: Did you see it?! This is my
power!

Zerachiel: If you learn your lesson from
this, promise me you won't cause any
more trouble--

Zerachiel: (A forbidden spell that
should be beyond the capabilities of
humans...)

Zerachiel: Effy, who cursed you? You
know, don't you?!

Zerachiel: No, I can't speak properly...
If it continues like this, I'll die...

Zerachiel: (If it's Aries, she might be
able to help...)

Zerachiel: (But, is it okay for me to
help this person...)

Zerachiel: (These are the ones who
humiliated my brethren... me.)

Zerachiel: (Even though I have reasons
to resent, I have no reason to help...)
Zerachiel: Effy, I might be a fool.

Zerachiel: Here, let me lend you my
shoulder.

Zerachiel: I don't want to help you...
but I can't just overlook it.

Zerachiel: Don't misunderstand, this is
just a loan.

Zerachiel: I'll help you, so make sure
to repay the favor.

Zerachiel: Well, I'm not expecting much
though...

Zerachiel: No, this isn't it... Wait,
what kind of book are you reading?

On [Month] [Day]: On my 9th birthday, a
clergyman came to our house. He said he
wanted to take me in.

My parents are greedy for money. They
happily sold me to the religious
organization.

Even so, I still feel guilty. The words
'It's for your own good' won't leave my
mind.

On [Month] [Day]: The clergymen
approached me and expressed their desire
to appoint me as a saint.

It seems that the reason is because I am
intersex.

It seems that being intersex is a
requirement to become a saint in the
Orpheus religious organization.

I have no interest in the position of a
saint, but I do hold resentment towards
my parents.

On [Month] [Day]: I was scheduled to
meet with the religious leader in order
to officially become a saint.

The religious leader had their face
hidden behind a mask. It was eerie, but
they didn't take an intimidating
attitude towards young me.

The gaze behind the mask is scary. I
wonder why.

On [Month] [Day]: Since receiving the
ceremony of becoming a saint, my
physical condition has been strange.

I immediately started to feel shortness
of breath and a pain running through my
chest.

Could it be an illness? However, the
diagnosis results are good.

And also, the religious leader came to
visit.
Do you not know the Seventh Curse?
I wonder what the Seventh Curse is.

On [Month] [Day]: Several years have
passed, and the number of bedridden days
has increased.

I might die if things continue like
this.
I don't have much longer to live...

On [Month] [Day]: I received a divine
revelation from the religious leader.

Be careful, as an angelic girl will soon
come to the religious organization.

On [Month] [Day]: An intruder appeared
in the religious organization. They said
they came to rescue their fellow angel.

She must be the angel that the religious
leader was talking about.

I'm surprised that angels actually
exist.

However, there are still lingering
doubts.

I wonder what they're misunderstanding,
even though our religious organization
has never captured an angel.

I tried to persuade her to quietly turn
back, but she didn't listen.

I reluctantly dealt with her using
binding magic. Following the punishment
regulations of the religious
organization, I decided to send her to
the underground torture chamber. How
pitiful...

But I hold no grudge against the girl. I
quietly gave instructions to ensure that
only her life is spared.

I have received instructions from the
religious leader to execute her, but she
is still a young girl.

Unlike me, she has a future. I didn't
want to take her life.

The girl's name seems to be Zerachiel.
It's an unusual name.

I hope for her rehabilitation in the
future.
Zerachiel: Wait... What do you mean?

Zerachiel: The religious organization
has never captured an angel? But, there
was definitely an angel right in front
of me...

Zerachiel: And, the saint helped me, you
say?

Zerachiel: Why would you do such a
thing...

Zerachiel: (To begin with, the reason I
came here... was because of that
person's request...)

Zerachiel: No, my head is all tangled
up...

Zerachiel: Maybe I should talk to Aries
about it...
Let's go back to the base.
